two weibull cdf: 1-e-(t/a)^gammma
```{r}
weibullCDF2<-function(data,a,g) {
  1-exp(-(data/a)^g)
}
```

```{r}
x<-seq(from=0,to=1.5,length.out = 1000)
y<-weibullCDF2(x,a=1,10)
plot(x,y,typ='l')
```
